The full text of every license used anywhere in this repository lives in the
LICENSES/ directory. Per-subtree license OVERRIDES are declared authoritatively
(and machine-readably) in REUSE.toml, and mirrored by a LICENSE file inside each
overridden subtree:

    api/       Apache-2.0    public OpenAPI / Protobuf contracts
    docs/      CC-BY-4.0     documentation & prose
    .agents/   MIT           agent skills & workflow tooling
    tools/     MIT           developer tooling

The authoritative, machine-readable license map is REUSE.toml. Verify the whole
tree with:

    reuse lint

Full default license text: LICENSES/AGPL-3.0-only.txt
